  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Shas'la T'au Kais, a Fire-Caste trooper fresh from the trial of fire, drops onto Dolumar IV with a hunter-cadre sent to rescue Aun'el Ko'vash — an Ethereal who has crash-landed behind Imperial lines. A clean extraction tangles into a multi-faction nightmare: Imperial Guard and Astartes hold the surface, a Chaos cult below the city has engineered Ko'vash's capture as bait for the soul-substance to free the Greater Daemon Tarkh'ax from a buried fragment of the Webway, and an Inquisition strike-team converges in pursuit. Kais cuts through every layer of betrayal, his caste-discipline fracturing under the rising kill-count. Tie-in novelisation of THQ's 2003 PlayStation 2 game; a rare Tau-POV anchor in early-2000s Black Library.",
